        " : «اَلْعُمْرَةُ مَفْرُوضَةٌ مِثْلُ اَلْحَجِّ فَإِذَا أَدَّى اَلْمُتْعَةَ فَقَدْ أَدَّى اَلْعُمْرَةَ اَلْمَفْرُوضَةَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2941 - Al-Mufaddal ibn Salih narrated from Abu Basir, from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"Umrah is an obligation like Hajj. When one performs Tamattu‘, they have fulfilled the obligatory Umrah.\""
